rc=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:16:25.000Z","msg":"人仔食仔架"},{"pid":"3785b8581be81b06d1a11dda358e8e0705f61719","tid":970750,"uid":2078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c029f8e75ef902cfe438802a73f09b649b93c9c7","tid":970750,"uid":177039,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:00:34.000Z","msg":"成班on9 投資有賺有蝕 蝕左就要攞返本金咁仲投咩資<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T12:01:01.000Z","msg":"雷曼咪係例子囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3fb3d9e1b1593c3947137ef6406d6e48fad4a9","tid":970750,"uid":31907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T12:45:13.000Z","msg":"查到資金來源係洗黑錢做第二個楊家誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56079ca9d89b8c334bafd3819bee3517c3a6d5c","tid":970750,"uid":51583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:46:19.000Z","msg":"幣少係自己PAGE係咁POST人地電話號碼等資料<br />\n真係好人有限<br />\n又有區議員被恐嚇<br />\n有排玩<br />\n不過明顯佢宜家開始想發老皮了<br />\n希望快D拆佢檔"},{"pid":"7837c90ece42fca55a8ce51122d83905f8d4878b","tid":970750,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:48:27.000Z","msg":"屌買債券聲稱有十厘回報果堆都要詳細考慮啦<br />\n更何況買礦機? 包生仔咩"},{"pid":"42cc944283083e03797959a3f0c9038e6454622c","tid":970750,"uid":155253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"比人呃果D快D去死啦,蠢撚個隻豬<br />\n最好比人呃果D扲唔返錢,幣少又被人斬死就最好啦"}]}